    <title>腾讯公益 404 页面介绍和代码使用</title>
    <link href="http://www.huangzijian888.cn/2018/12/404/"/>
    <id>http://www.huangzijian888.cn/2018/12/404/</id>
    <published>2018-12-22T12:35:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-12-23T14:44:50.915Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>腾讯公益 404 页面是由腾讯公司员工志愿者自主发起的互联网公益活动。网站只需要在自己的 404 页面中嵌入一段简单的代码，就能通过互联网来迅速传播失踪儿童信息，从而提高找回失踪儿童的概率。失踪儿童信息来自宝贝回家寻子网。腾讯公益 404 页面，寻找丢失儿童，让大家一起关注此项公益事业！<br>效果如下：<a href="http://huangzijian888.cn/404.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://huangzijian888.cn/404.html</a><a id="more"></a></p><p>使用方法，新建 404.html 页面，放到 <strong>source</strong> 目录下，内容如下：<br><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>404 - 黄子健's blog<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"description"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"404错误，页面消失啦！"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="string">"content-type"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"text/html;charset=utf-8;"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="string">"X-UA-Compatible"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"IE=edge,chrome=1"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"robots"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"all"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"robots"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"index,follow"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">"icon"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"/favicon.ico"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text/javascript"</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"//qzonestyle.gtimg.cn/qzone/hybrid/app/404/search_children.js"</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span> <span class="attr">homePageUrl</span>=<span class="string">"http://www.huangzijian888.cn"</span> <span class="attr">homePageName</span>=<span class="string">"回到我的主页"</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>更多参考：<br><a href="https://www.qq.com/404/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公益 404 页面-腾讯网</a></p>]]></content>
    
